Running Lidar d435i on Ros2, Rviz2

ROS 2 humble is installed, 


1. Connect Camera to Ross
Launch RealSenese 
(source is ROS2)
	source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash
	ros2 launch realsense2_camera rs_launch.py pointcloud.enable:=true

Output: Node is up (means the system is running) 

2. Open RViz2
(source is ROS2)
	source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash
	rviz2

TO run Camera and PointCloud
  -Fixed Frame: camera_link

  Add
   By topic
      - /camera  
        -/camera 
            -image_raw
              camera
      - /depth
        - /color
          - /points
              PointCloud2

    
